<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FilmFiesta 2025 - Dheera</title>
  <style>
    /* General Reset */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #121212;
      background-image: url('https://resizing.flixster.com/xf1SmRgwTZhhPgIMwuwDbD8LgrA=/fit-in/352x330/v2/https://resizing.flixster.com/-XZAfHZM39UwaGJIFWKAE8fS0ak=/v3/t/assets/p3622446_k_h9_aa.jpg');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-attachment: fixed;
      background-color: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.8); /* Adds a dark overlay */
      background-blend-mode: overlay;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
      width: 95%;
      max-width: 400px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); /* Semi-transparent container */
      background-image: url('https://img.freepik.com/premium-vector/flat-design-old-film-background_23-2150995815.jpg?semt=ais_hybrid'); /* Background pattern */
      background-size: cover;
      color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
      border-radius: 15px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0px 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
      margin: 50px;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); /* Semi-transparent header */
      background-image: url('https://img.freepik.com/premium-vector/flat-design-old-film-background_23-2150995815.jpg?semt=ais_hybrid'); /* Header texture */
      color: white;
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
      box-shadow: 0px 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }

    .header img {
      position: absolute;
      top: 15px;
      left: 20px;
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .header .college-name {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 5px 0;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    }

    .header .union-name {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .header .presents {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-style: italic;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .header .event-name {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin: 15px 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .poster {
      width: 100%;
      position: relative;
    }

    .poster img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    .movie-details {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .movie-details h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .movie-details p {
      margin: 5px 0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .ticket-button {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      background-color: #e33030;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 0 0 15px 15px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .ticket-button:hover {
      background-color: #ff4a4a;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
        width: 95%;
      }

      .header img {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        top: 10px;
        left: 10px;
      }

      .header .college-name {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .header .union-name {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .header .event-name {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div class="header">
      <p class="college-name">MARYMATHA ARTS AND SCIENCE COLLEGE</p>
      <h3 class="union-name">SAMATVA COLLEGE UNION</h3>
      <p class="presents">presents</p>
      <h4 class="event-name">FilmFiesta</h4>
    </div>

    <!-- Poster Section -->
    <div class="poster">
      <img src=https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYjA1MTVkYzUtMjc0NS00ZTdjLWI0ZTQtNjQ0ZDFkMThhNTFjXkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_.jpg" alt="Dheera Poster">
    </div>

    <!-- Movie Details Section -->
    <div class="movie-details">
      <h2>Dheera (2009)</h2>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= movies[0].date %></p>
      <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= movies[0].time %> PM</p>
      <p><strong>Language:</strong> Malayalam</p>
      <p><strong>Duration:</strong>  2h 46m</p>
      <p>A street-bike racer chances upon a woman and is struck by visions of a past life where they were both star-crossed lovers in a war-ridden kingdom 400 years ago, while the reincarnation of his romantic rival emerges with murderous intent.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Reserve Tickets Button -->
    <a href="/reserve/<%= movies[0]._id %>" class="ticket-button">Reserve Tickets</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
